text: Watch for this Folsom High, Stanford grad playing in Super Bowl 51 Feb 04, 2017 Jordan Richards will take the field for the New England Patriots vs. the Atlanta Falcons in Super Bowl 51, Feb. 5, 2017, but he started his life and football career here in Folsom.
